HEADWORD: Wildwood
<hw>Wild"wood</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A wild or
unfrequented wood. Also used adjectively; <as>as, <ex>wildwood</ex>
flowers; <ex>wildwood</ex> echoes</as>.</def>
